{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong><i>Please note that this game is currently in development, and all graphics/gameplay elements are a work in progress. If you see something you don't like or something that isn't there, chances are it will change!</i></strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3438850/extras/join_the_discord_w_link.gif?t=1738992611\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Sledding Game</strong> is a cozy, online multiplayer game about sledding, relaxing, and hanging out with your friends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Sled the Slopes</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Carve your way through snowy trails, hit jumps, and rack up points as you explore the slopes. Whether you're racing to the bottom or taking it slow, the hill is all about fun, friends, and freedom.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3438850/extras/sleddby.gif?t=1738992611\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Customizable Characters</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Sled in style with fully customizable animal characters + expressions!</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Frog</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Penguin</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Polar Bear (in development)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">+ Many more in progress</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3438850/extras/charactercustomizationpenguinfrog.gif?t=1738992611\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Chat Away</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Chat with friends using built-in <strong>proximity voice chat</strong> or text chat. Whether you're cheering someone on mid-sled or racing down the hill, communication is seamless and fun.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Chill Without Sledding (in development)</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Need a break from the cold? Head to the cabin to warm up, hang out with friends, and grab some cocoa. You can also try fun minigames, either inside the cabin or out in the snow.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Snowball fights</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Drinking hot cocoa (and other cozy cabin delights)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Snowmen making (and breaking)</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3438850/extras/runaroundfrog.gif?t=1738992611\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Ragdoll Physics</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Wipeouts have never been so funny! Enjoy dynamic ragdoll physics that make every tumble down the hill a memorable moment.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3438850/extras/ragdollhitsled.gif?t=1738992611\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Clothing / Sleds</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Purchase cosmetics by earning points on the mountain.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Clothing accessories (hats, jackets, scarves, goggles...etc)\u00a0 (in development)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Sled customization ranging from different bonuses for different sleds, or just adding stickers to your favorite sled.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3438850/extras/hatsandsleds.gif?t=1738992611\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Community-Driven Multiplayer</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Join public or private lobbies to sled with friends or meet new ones. Sit on a bench with a homie, or race down the hill with your group. With up to 100* players, the ski-lift could get quite the line.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3438850/extras/benchfrogsandfriend.gif?t=1738992611\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">*I'm hoping I can do 100 player lobbies, but until further testing, this will just be a guess</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Credits</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Music:\u00a0Introverted Spacemen, IMLAZY</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Logo Art:\u00a0Addy G Brown</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">fwog</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3438850/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738992611","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3438850/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1738992611","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3438850/9da85eb9a065f48c4410a4a1ba3f819cf54b14fe/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738992611","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3438850/9da85eb9a065f48c4410a4a1ba3f819cf54b14fe/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738992611","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong><i>Please note that this game is currently in development, and all graphics/gameplay elements are a work in progress. If you see something you don't like or something that isn't there, chances are it will change!</i></strong></h2><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3438850/extras/join_the_discord_w_link.gif?t=1738992611\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Sledding Game</strong> is a